\begin_layout Plain Layout
Q4
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
How long can you wait for a video to be loaded before giving up?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In general, people are able to bear a short delay if they use torrent (
 usually promise of good quality) or if the video is expected by the user.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It would be a good idea to favor the quality videos and expected ones, with
 a “like” system or with some ranking for a for example.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Float figure
