\begin_layout Paragraph
Are you annoyed by advertisements?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Most of the people do not like advertisement but almost 30% do not care
 about it.
 The graphic expressly show a reject of advertisement from most of the people.
 However it is usually the main source of revenues to finance the video
 storage.
 
\end_layout

