\begin_layout Paragraph
How much time do you spend on watching videos per day?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We have mean of 2 hours of watching per people a day.
 Moreover, 40% of the asked people are watching between 30 minutes and one
 hour of video content daily.
 Single videos hosted may not exceed 2 hours.
\end_layout

